{"tid":2080840,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想知點推國際戰線既手足入黎 入紙師分享當年今日","createTime":"2020-06-26T17:49:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T18:08:46.000Z","uid":216571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"581d1270b8fb0d704729a91e1d22674f03838f2b","tid":2080840,"uid":216571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T17:49:42.000Z","msg":"舊年今日國際戰線蓄勢待發 今日已經略有小成<br />\n從零開始 香港人真係好勁<br />\n不卑不亢 莊敬自強<br />\n一息尚存 抗爭到底<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地仲要煲底見</span></span><br />\n<br />\n 《入紙師是如何煉成的？》&mdash; 劉頴匡<br />\n/過去一年，我堅持將本土抗爭路線付諸實踐，前後舉辦十幾次大大小小的遊行集會，甚至被連登仔戲稱為「入紙師」。很多人不知道的是，其實在上年626的領事館馬拉松請願之前，我是毫無入紙經驗的。<br />\n<br />\n在此回顧一下成為入紙師的歷程，以及我對本地和國際戰線的一些想法。//<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1363944197109305&amp;id=609505342553198\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1363944197109305%26id%3D609505342553198&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2h%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=61fa4be7\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1363944197109305&amp;id=609505342553198</a>"},{"pid":"e34747e6e0c0ca9251af344564eb58ccf93d71db","tid":2080840,"uid":216571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T17:54:47.000Z","msg":"push 1"},{"pid":"7798772025385a66f743224b3fc839353a69aabf","tid":2080840,"uid":216571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T18:01:17.000Z","msg":"push 2"},{"pid":"ef19774af4b4e96e36b77c937d2c03e5dbee7b47","tid":2080840,"uid":216571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T18:04:53.000Z","msg":"push 3"},{"pid":"ec43ffbef33637960c588dba323710b4d6e17411","tid":2080840,"uid":216571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T18:08:46.000Z","msg":"push 4"}]}